RawLine: SDM_2103023101,【「回想當年，我奉命率禁軍準備北上迎敵，駐紮於陳橋驛，當晚酒喝多了就睡了。」】,【「回想当年，我奉命率禁军准备北上迎敌，驻扎于陈桥驿，当晚酒喝多了就睡了。」】

Items.mt: <[>"Back in the day, when I was ordered to lead the forbidden army to prepare for the enemy in the north, I was stationed at Chenqiao, and I fell asleep that night after drinking too much wine. <]>
